            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I found Poro, but I lost track of her..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I see. Thank you for letting me know, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I'm sorry I couldn't bring her back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Don't apologize. The ways of the stars have decided her fate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Th-The stars?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "In the night sky. Do you know how the stars make complicated movements? Just like a sprocket."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Every living thing in this world has a star, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "The movement of the stars decide our fate, or so the saying goes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "So it's not your fault Poro disappeared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Plus, I'm glad to know she seemed to be doing fine on her own."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x48,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I was so worried about leaving her alone, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "If your sister's gonna be at her side, it's reassuring."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for worrying about Poro, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "(She's trying to be enthusiastic, but I think she's still depressed...)"
        }
    ]
}